{"title":"忆·灾·荒","authors":["韩修琏","王广庆"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":7,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"忆·灾·荒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起来，真凄惨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四二四三灾荒年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家时光没法办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"房产、地土、衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"服、家俱都卖干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头等水地几十块，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱地卖不上十块钱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好棹好柜十斤米，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣服布匹不值钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就那样也是没人要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才到山西逃荒年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣裳布匹背多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换回一包罗卜片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们受了多少罪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌伪还要坑害咱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是打来又是骂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"结果东西逼个干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍饥挨饿回家转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"居家大小泪涟涟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪涟涟，没法办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重打饥荒去逃难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤土沟里下煤窑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罐台窑上去推罐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来身上没有劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头＠眼黑不能干；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腰酸腿软不济事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一时不防倒栽蒜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲儿亲女他乡卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恩爱夫妻两失散。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越思越想越心酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快备荒来抗旱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽说近来下了点雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光靠这点也不粘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快抢种，勤锄苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多种秋菜争模范。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少齐动手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合力战胜灾荒年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家跟着共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着政府的法儿办，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不逃难去受苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打败老蒋战胜天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩修琏  王广庆作"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}